Look at this. We spent most of the game stuck in our own half between AWB and Scott and no right side winger coming to help. This has been a problem for years and years and years. That heatmap is disgusting. https://t.co/SxHcLpRTDH

His qualities on ball, interplay, and ability to sustain possession are the exact qualities missing today. It‚Äôs not say Mason shouldn‚Äôt be playing, but teams have identified this issue and we have to resort once again to long through balls.
